'''Baden Lathe''' was a [[Captain/Legends|captain]] in [[New Republic Intelligence Service]].

==Biography==
A member of the [[Analysis Bureau (New Republic Intelligence)|Analysis Bureau]], Lathe was responsible for compiling a report on the events leading to the marriage of [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], including a dossier on [[Warlord/Legends|Warlord]] [[Zsinj]] and his forces, information on the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]], and as much data as was available about the [[Witches of Dathomir]]. Lathe did all he could to overcome the spotty nature of [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomiri]] records and the secretive tendencies of the [[Hapan]]s. Lathe was extremely pleased at being granted the opportunity to interact with the "Heroes of [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Yavin]] and [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]" and expressed his regret to [[General/Legends|General]] [[Airen Cracken/Legends|Airen Cracken]] about the possibility of error in his report.

